title: Tribe Archipelago Signature Presets
description:
Tribe Archipelago Signature Presets

- ACR
- Lightroom

Presets or Develop Presets, are custom settings used in Adobe Lightroom to produce particular effect on your images.
You simply click the Preset and it will automatically adjust the settings on your image to create a certain look/tone.
Using presets will not only speed up your workflow, it will also provide consistency in your work.

 
http://tribearchipelago.com
